S4.title: 12 hour☘️ Study with me LIVE ☕ calm cozy ambience🩺POMODORO🔥Real-time study #Medgirl 2025-04-05 16:05
S4.description:
📩open me:

Hi!
Welcome to another Study with me
Thanks for joining
_________________________

I hope this study video helps you avoid using social media while you study. You will find a quiet and cosy study room ambience in this video when studying at your home. Hopefully, this would get you motivated more for studying. You might hear the rain, birds, typing sounds and the flipping of pages (and cars too, unfortunately) from time to time, and I hope that helps you know that I'm there studying with you!

🔥Key to success - """"BE CONSISTENT""""🔥

___________________________

What are you studying and where are you joining from? I also wonder what type of videos you like, study at the library or study at home? Your opinions are quite important to me; and, if you let me know what type of videos you like to watch, I would be happy. 
_____________________________

✧･ﾟ at the beginning of the study sessions, make sure to:
- turn off anything you're not going to be using to study
- have your materials ready to go
- have drinks/food ready so you don't have to get up to go get necessities
- have a clear idea of what you want to accomplish during the session (i.e., choose a task from your to-do list)


✧･ﾟ during the breaks:
- stop working as soon as the timer hits, even if you're mid-sentence
- make sure to get up, do some simple stretches
- refill anything that needs to get refilled
- talk to friends/update family

✧･ﾟ at the end of this video:
if you want to continue studying, give yourself a longer break and you can the next session video!

you're set to go! ♡
_____________________________
💡Please adjust the volume for each of the background music that comes out.
The ASMR that comes out with 💡 is the sound of burning wood and Rain. 
_____________________________

We have a Chat bot- 🤖
Commands for chat bot- 

!hi - when you join in👋
!start - to start studying
!top - Top Points
!points -  to know your points💯
!complete - when done with the goal

Chat rules:
- Being nice and respectful is mandatory!
- Spamming, harassment, trolling, bullying, repeating and all capital messages are definitely prohibited!
- Please feel encouraged to write in English so no one would feel excluded in the chat :)
- Please check YouTube's Community Guidelines
_____________________________

To those who are starting :
In order to study or do anything for long periods of time you need a strong purpose and you must be willing to endure challenges. If I can do this, think about what you can accomplish. If you're starting out, start from low intervals(10-30 minutes) and gradually increase once you feel you're comfortable. If you feel like quitting, visualize your goals and evaluate your purpose. Learn to accept challenges in your life to become uncommon.

🔴 Welcome to our LIVE Study With Me Session! 📚✨
Hi! We are Pallavi (ON LIVE) & Ayush , CA Final aspirants on a mission to clear the exams. Join me for a focused and productive study session, where we study together, stay accountable, and crush our goals! 🚀

TODAY'S TO-DO LIST
🔳 Audit revision for mock exam 

🗓️ Schedule for Live Sessions (GMT +5:30)
🌞 Morning Session: 8:00 AM – 5:00 PM
🌙 Evening Session: 6:30 PM – 9:00 PM

🔴 Disclaimer 🔴
We do not promote or advertise any of the components in the video, such as Notes, Classes, Books, Laptop, or any type of brand. 😊

📌 Join Our Study Community!
📢 WhatsApp - https://chat.whatsapp.com/HIdo30Qtzta5zEGO5Lu39r
________________________________________

❓ Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs) 💡

•  Who are we? 🙋‍♀️🙋‍♂️
Pallavi & Ayush, CA Finalists 🎓

•  Who are you studying with on LIVE? 👩‍💻
I’m Pallavi and I’m 24 years old. 🎂

•  Where are we from? 🇮🇳
Odisha, India 📍

• How can we connect with you? 🤳
Join our whatsapp community, the link is above!!

•  What exams are we preparing for? 📝
CA Final May '25 exam (Group 1 Only)-2nd attempt. 🤞

• Did you appear for both the groups previously?
No, only Group 1. Yet to appear for group 2. 

•  What is the Pomodoro Technique during the study sessions? ⏱️
The Pomodoro technique is a time management method based on 55-minute stretches of focused work broken by 5 to 10 minute breaks 🍅

•  What laptop do you use? 💻
Acer ALG laptop.

•  What phone and tablet do you use for streaming? 📱 🖥️
Streaming via OnePlus 9RT & Samsung S6 Lite tablet.

•  How can I connect with you? 🔗
Join our WhatsApp community! Link is above !! 📲

•  Why no music during live sessions? 🔇
No time for integration due to exams ; silent mode preferred by most of the audience 👬👫

•  How many hours do we study? 📚
8 to 10 hours a day ⏳

•  How many hours do we sleep? 😴
6 to 7 hours a day 🛌

•  What is the timer app on my Tablet? ⏱️
Its called Track it (not sponsoring the app).

•  Can I ask questions during the session? 🙋
Yes, feel free to ask! 🗣️

•  What if I can’t attend the live session? 📺
Watch the recorded session later. 🎥

•  Can I join this session if I’m not preparing for CA exams? 🧑‍🎓
Yes, anyone can join! 🎉

If you have any other doubts, let me know in the comment section!! 👇💬

S17.title: study with me 24/7 | pomodoro 50/10 | study together | rain background + music in break 2025-04-05 16:05
S17.description:
This 24/7 stream from Studyistic is designed to motivate students anywhere, anytime! The study sessions are broadcast live, this makes it possible to study together at the same time with students from all over the world! You might even meet someone who studies the same as you but is 3000 km away from you. How 🆒 isn't this? Feel free to post a message in the chat and in no time you will have a whole group of study friends with you!😍

📌📌HOW TO USE THIS STREAM?
📖During the study sessions (always 50 minutes), study as hard as you can!🫡 
📢Then in the 10-minute break there is room for relaxation. During the break, there are many students who tell in the chat how their session was, what the plans are for the next session, or just something fun they want to share. Sharing with others in the chat what the plans are for the other sessions can be extra motivating. 

📌📌CHAT COMMANDS
🔆!weather city ⇾ Check the weather in your city.
🔆!quote ⇾ get a motivational quote in the chat.
🔆!welcome ⇾ For new subscribers/study buddies.
🔆!hug ⇾ Get a virtual hug.
🔆!instagram ⇾ Follow me on Instagram.
🔆Put a motivational message/quote in the chat and maybe it will be at the ⭐top of the chat⭐.

📌📌PRACTICAL THINGS OF THE STREAM
🔆My Study method 🍅: 50 min study & 10 min breaks.
🔆Stream Schedule 📅: Check my channel banner (timezone UTC +  02:00):  @Studyistic_Laura  
🔆Please keep the chat in English!
🔆In the stream there is always rain music. Do you want to listen🔊 something else? At the bottom⬇️ of this description there are some links for you. 
🔆Link to the discord: https://discord.gg/Vpms958qrN

📌📌ABOUT ME
🔆Name: Laura
🔆Age: 24
🔆Location: Belgium
🔆Studying: PhD in wireless communications at KU Leuven (Campus Bruges)
🔆Languages: English, French and Dutch
🔆What do I do in my free time? Swimming, go for a walk with Blacky, 📡Licensed radio amateur
🔆Wake up at: 7-8 AM
🔆Go sleeping at: 9:30 PM
🔆Future plans: I want to specialise in high-frequency technology📡
🔆Link to instagram: https://www.instagram.com/studyistic_laura

📌📌PETS 
🔆 Moestie🐱 (grey cat and is blind) -- 13 years old
🔆 Poeske🐱 (Dutch for Kitty, she lost a piece of her tail when she was little) -- 3,5 years old
🔆 Pluis 🐱-- 2 year old

By joining a study stream, you build a habit of discipline and consistency. Seeing others study in real-time keeps you accountable and motivated. The shared energy of a virtual study space helps improve focus, making productivity feel effortless.

- My goal is 8 to 10h of intense, distraction-free study everyday. Can you match the focus? Let’s push our limits. Stay disciplined, and achieve your academic goals together! My Daily schedule👉 https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1UtDY5KiHaYuJoCtNW0fnkMOucu-xHsKMNVRRk1vQ6us/edit?usp=sharing

🚀 How I Study👇
- I follow the Pomodoro technique 60 mins of focused study + 10 mins break🎯 with Fire sounds for better concentration. If you're looking for a study-buddy, join me, and let's stay consistent together! We’re building a focused study community where productivity is the first priority.

Live-Chat Rules👇
- Replies only during breaks – Stay focused
- Keep chat positive & study-related
- Support & motivate each other

Live-Chat Commands👇(https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/10_MNW2EaZOREZJpBKeLw0kgc3u9IbI-WbULGzKGSuHE/edit?usp=sharing)
-   !start – Begin your study session
-   !break – Take a break
-   !done – End your study & rest
-   !points – Check your study points
-   !schedule – View my stream schedule/timetable
-   !telegram – Get my Telegram channel link
-   !whatsapp – Get my WhatsApp channel link
-   !biodata – View my basic info
-   !location – Check my location
-   !commands – See all available commands
-   !discord – Join my study room on Discord

Hi! it's me Rahul 🙋

This is the study with me session and here we use the pomodoro technique for studying. Pomodoro technique is one of the most effective studying technique which helps you to boost your focus and productivity while studying. Here we apply the 60/10 format (60 minutes study and 10 minutes break). During break time feel free to chitchat with me in live chat. 

Don't forget to keep water bottle by your side and stay hydrated!

: https://www.instagram.com/_rahuldevkota/


For inquires
: rahulenter22@gmail.com





💭Thoughts and purpose of this channel:

In today's world it's so difficult to congregate your focus for a particular work. There are distractions everywhere and it's too easy to lose your self-consciousness to these distractions. During this period of engrossment, It becomes essential for us to take back our consciousness and get out of the pool of distractions which seems pleasureful to swim in but is slowly submerging us into it. Best way to avoid these things is to be conscious and engage yourself in the activity which is actually important to you. It is the exact purpose of this channel. This channel is rooted onto the foundation of making progress and helping other to make progress. 

Personally, I get motivated by watching other people study. I've been watching these "study with me" sessions of other youtubers from long ago (until I started my own), and being honest, it helped me a lot. I am heartily thankful for those youtubers who helped me to make my study effective and I can confront that they created a positive impact in my life. Since I'm in their place right now, I can't be more happier than to be able to make the same positive impact on other people's life. There is a quotation saying "Helping others is the way we help ourselves". I feel that helping people and being able to make a positive impact in other people's life is the greatest thing a human can do. So, I think that you have understood the soul purpose of creating this channel.

Also, not to forget that this channel is highly inspired by 'James Scholz' who is the original founder and god of 'Study with me' videos. 'Pascal Zoels', '7viksthan' are other popular YouTubers who post similar contents (ps. they are my favorite)

S72.description:
"هل تجد صعوبة في المذاكرة وحدك؟ 🤔💡 انضم إلينا في هذا البث المباشر للمذاكرة الجماعية! 🎯📚 سنذاكر معًا في أجواء هادئة ومحفزة، لنزيد من تركيزنا وننجز مهامنا بفعالية. احضر كتبك، جهّز قهوتك ☕، واضبط مؤقتك ⏳ – حان وقت الإنتاجية! 🚀✨ لا تنسَ مشاركة البث مع أصدقائك لنذاكر سويًا! 💪📖"
📚 أهمية "Study with me" 📚

نظام "Study with me" يوفر بيئة تفاعلية ومحفزة للدراسة. من خلال الانضمام لجلسات دراسية مشتركة، يمكنك:

تعزيز التركيز: البيئة المشتركة تساعد على تقليل التشتت وزيادة الإنتاجية.
تحفيز الإلهام: رؤية الآخرين يعملون يمكن أن تكون دافعًا قويًا لمواصلة المذاكرة.
بناء الروتين: الالتزام بمواعيد محددة للدراسة يساهم في تنظيم الوقت.
الدعم المتبادل: مشاركة التحديات والنصائح مع زملائك تساعد على تخطي العقبات.
📖 بنذاكر بتقنية بومودورو 50/10! 📖

تعتبر تقنية بومودورو 50/10 من أفضل الطرق لتحسين إنتاجيتك في الدراسة. تعتمد على:

50 دقيقة تركيز: خصص 50 دقيقة للدراسة بتركيز تام. اجعل هذه الفترة خالية من المشتتات.
10 دقائق استراحة: بعد كل 50 دقيقة، خذ 10 دقائق للاسترخاء. يمكنك القيام بتمارين بسيطة أو شرب كوب من الماء.
لماذا تعمل هذه الطريقة؟

زيادة الإنتاجية: يساعد التناوب بين التركيز والاستراحة في تعزيز القدرة على التحصيل.
تجنب الإرهاق: الاستراحات القصيرة تمنحك الطاقة للاستمرار.
تحسين التركيز: فترات العمل الطويلة تجعل عقلك أكثر استجابة واستعدادًا للتعلم.
جرب تقنية بومودورو 50/10 اليوم وراقب كيف ستتحسن نتائجك! 🌟
